A4.text: Falange Española (FE) was a Spanish fascist and national syndicalist political organization active from 1933 to 1934.

A5.text: Founded on October 29, 1933 by Alfonso García Valdecasas, Julio Ruiz de Alda, and José Antonio Primo de Rivera, the eldest son of the deceased dictator Miguel Primo de Rivera.
